sub_title: Lead Entertainment Host at Holland America Line
summary:
The study Tourism and Leisure management provided me with a high level of knowledge in different areas of tourism. My work in the many different fields also gave me a lot of experience. 

For the past years, I have been working for the cruise line company, Holland America Line. I started off in the Guest Services department, which gave me a very broad and good perspective on cruising, and it's guests. 
At the moment I work within the Entertainment Department, which I love and do with a lot of passion. 

I am hospitable, enthusiastic, fast learning, stress resistant and social. Besides this I am always trying to push myself to achieve great results in both my professional and personal life.

Curious for my professional history? Please scroll down. Can’t you find something? Don’t hesitate to contact me.
